  "title": "Compare HVAC Quotes Side by Side | Woogoro",
  "bodyText": "Skip to main content\n✓ Free · No email · No phone · No signup · We never sell or share your data\nWoogoro\nGuides\nMethodology\nYou are comparing quotes.\nWant a free estimate first? →\nHave a single quote? Analyze →\nCompare your HVAC quotes\n\nUpload 2 or 3 HVAC quotes and we'll show you which one is the best value for the equipment, install scope, and warranty offered.\n\nParsing\nThis may take a moment\nParsing\nThis may take a moment\n📄\nQuote 3\nOptional\nStill parsing... 0 of 2 ready\nHow to compare HVAC quotes correctly\n\nHVAC quotes are notoriously hard to compare because contractors rarely quote the same equipment, tonnage, or install scope. A $7,000 quote and a $12,000 quote can be for wildly different systems — different SEER2 ratings, different brands, one with a Manual J load calculation and one without.\n\nThe price gap usually comes down to equipment tier (builder-grade vs two-stage vs variable speed), whether ductwork is being inspected or modified, and whether the install includes a new line set, pad, disconnect, and thermostat. A cheap quote with old ductwork and undersized returns will underperform forever.\n\nFocus on total installed cost for an apples-to-apples system, the labor warranty (1 year vs 10 year is a massive difference), and whether the contractor actually measured your home's load instead of just matching the old unit's tonnage.\n\nMost important fields to compare\nTotal installed cost\nEquipment brand & model number\nTonnage / BTU capacity\nSEER2 / AFUE efficiency rating\nManual J load calculation performed\nDuctwork inspection & modifications\nPermit & inspection included\nParts warranty (years)\nLabor warranty (years)\nNew refrigerant line set\nOld unit haul-off\nThermostat included\nHelpful HVAC Guides\nHVAC quote analyzer\nHVAC cost guide\nPopular metros for HVAC pricing\n\nCity pages with metro-specific HVAC cost ranges, contractor signals, and quote benchmarks.\n\nNew York, NY\nLos Angeles, CA\nChicago, IL\nHouston, TX\nPhoenix, AZ\nDallas, TX\nAtlanta, GA\nDenver, CO\nSeattle, WA\nAustin, TX\nGET A PRICE\nGet an estimate\nAnalyze a quote\nCompare quotes\nRoof estimate\nBROWSE\nAll cities\nCost guides\nFind contractors\nMedical cost lookup\nTOP TRADES\nRoofing\nHVAC\nPlumbing\nElectrical\nSolar\nAuto repair\nABOUT\nAbout Woogoro\nMethodology\nAccessibility\nPrivacy\nTerms\n\nWoogoro helps people analyze HVAC contractor quotes, compare prices, and check costs against benchmark rates. Privacy | About | Methodology | Contact\n\nOperated by Woogoro LLC, a South Carolina limited liability company · 17064 Laurelmont Court, Fort Mill, SC 29707",
